Amanda", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "CRM System Update", "from": "robert.hayes@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Robert Hayes", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["james.parker@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2023-04-02 09:30:00", "body": "Hi Amanda,

