Regards,
Robert", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "New Compliance Training", "from": "linda.jones@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Linda Jones", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionautomotive.com", "karen.morris@elexionautomotive.com", "daniel.adams@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-02 13:15:00", "body": "Hello all,

