Linda", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_004", "subject": "Electric Vehicle Industry Summit", "from": "sarah.mitchell@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Sarah Mitchell", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["karen.morris@elexionautomotive.com", "daniel.adams@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2023-04-03 10:45:00", "body": "Hi Amanda,

